elements.name: Como autor creo un post como draft, y después lo publico

steps.name: I send a signal to user 2 containing "logged"
I go to new post form
I send a signal to user 2 containing "creating"
I create a post with title "$name_1" and content "$string_1"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "drafting"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "draft created"
I wait for a signal containing "checked hidden post" for 30 seconds
I select the listed post with name "$$name_1"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "publishing"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "post published"

name: Crear un post como borrador, revisar que un usuario no puede verlo, publicar el post, y revisarlo desde la vista de usuario
